'''Abirilyum''' ( Beryllum s Tindlizt) iga yan [[Afrḍis akimyan|ufrḍis akimi]] lli ilan tasdugmt n '''Be''' d uṭṭun afrḍas 4. Iga yat tidi imellɣden, idus, ifssus d ig yan walkin ircan. Innugger bahra ɣ iɣzwer, d tamtta n wakal illa gis 0.0004% n ufrḍis ad <ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beryllium</ref><ref>https://www.britannica.com/science/beryllium</ref>.

